OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry start
OL,6,Fwith some clear spells for Orkney.
OL,7,FOtherwise it will be cloudy through
OL,8,Fthe evening and overnight with a few
OL,9,Flight showers. Moderate to fresh winds
OL,10,Ffor Shetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA cooler day with some
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells and variable
OL,14,Fcloud. Mostly dry but the odd light
OL,15,Fshower possible in the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
